<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />終於到了萬聖節當天了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />距離下午5點正式開始還有一段時間，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經等不及啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你好像<delay8 />已經完全<delay8 />
沉浸在萬聖節氣氛裡了耶？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />我也是喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經練習好要怎麼嚇大家了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也要小心喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈，<delay20 /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />開玩笑的啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然活動期間<delay8 />要準備很多東西，<delay20 />
但是準備的過程<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也能成為美好的回憶哩。<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下午5點開始就是期待已久的萬聖節啦，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們<delay8 />都要盡情享受活動，
炒熱現場氣氛喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你準備好<delay20 />迎接萬聖節了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果還沒有，就快點去準備吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />活動5點就會開始囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">好，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也差不多要準備裝扮了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可要好好期待喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會把你嚇得<delay8 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />冷汗直冒的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />萬聖節馬上就要開始哩。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />活動開始前的這段時間，<delay8 />
果然會讓人心跳加速啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說我有看到島上<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />放著南瓜家具喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛好現在是萬聖節的時期，
看到那種裝飾<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就能感受到節慶氛圍，
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還挺不錯的呢。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說島上<delay8 />有放著南瓜家具喔，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有看到嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然數量還不多，<delay frames="40" />但能感受到
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />萬聖節的氛圍正逐漸升溫，
我還滿開心的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">話說這座島的景色……<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有好多南瓜裝飾，<delay8 />給人一種
萬聖節的感覺呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很期待活動當天喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這座島現在<delay8 />簡直就像是
為了萬聖節而存在的一樣，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到處都是南瓜家具<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當天到底會是怎樣的萬聖節呢？<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這下子<delay8 />可真是令人期待啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
</msbt>